<blockquote>
<p><a id="Stage38"><span style="font-size: 16pt;">39、Stage 38:</span></a><br><span style="font-size: 16pt;">页面如下：</span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size: 16pt;"><img src="/uploads/2021/12/ac1f62f379e58d2dccfb119080b43beb.png"></span><br><span style="font-size: 16pt;">密文：ADDFADAFAG</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16pt;">先看源码：</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16pt;"><img src="/uploads/2021/12/4ebcf577c4666eb3bcc0bbb4515c90b8.png"></span><br><span style="font-size: 16pt;">标题提示ADFGX 先了解下这个东西</span></p>
